<L>__{interior cullen house second floor landing night}
<A>__{alice tugs bella and edward to the top of the landing, then skips down the stairs. they look down into the living room hundreds of pink candles and rose filled crystal bowls. rosalie, esme, emmett, carlisle, jasper and alice look up at her, all of them stunningly beautiful. bella would love to disappear, but edward leads her down to the living room where esme and carlisle hug bella warmly.}
