<P>__{(aims the camera)}
<D>__{show me the love!}
<A>__{edward pulls bella into an embrace, they look deeply into one another's eyes. flash!}
<C>__{alice}
<D>__{for your scrapbook. now open your presents!}
<A>__{alice drags bella over to a table piled with elaborately wrapped gifts, a huge cake and a tall stack of china plates.}
