<D>__{alice, i'm the only one who even eats cake. that thing could feed fifty.}
<C>__{alice}
<D>__{hope you're hungry. here, this one's from emmett.}
<A>__{the others crowd around... jasper somewhat away. bella, no fan of being the center of attention, opens the gift to find an empty car radio box.}
<C>__{bella}
<D>__{um... thanks?}
