<D>__{i will take care of her, edward.}
<P>__{(edward doesn't move)}
<D>__{check on jasper. go.}
<A>__{edward looks from him to bella. then steps back, allowing carlisle to lift bella and carry her to the kitchen. but just before the kitchen door closes, bella sees edward's agonized face. he turns away, unable to meet her eyes...}
